      <span class="c3" style="color: #000000; font-family: 'Arial'; font-size: 11pt; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;">But a new Johns Hopkins study may have just uncovered the real cause of nerve damage.</span>
    </p>
